{"title":"达赉湖","authors":["黎焕颐"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":10,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"达赉湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎焕颐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖？湖？湖？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！不！不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么，是明珠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！也不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个强悍的民族，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在呼伦贝尔大草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向苍天袒开热气腾腾的肺腑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，巨大的欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着巨大的痛苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在蓝天碧野之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛起伏……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"假若我是放牧草原的骑手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会把我的全部——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱与恨，灵与肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝结而成的块垒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给鼎沸的达赉湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去蒸，去煮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒸透，煮熟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，远天帆影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与星月共舞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！假若我是逐云追风的猎人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我决不只是弯弓射大雕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还会袒开宽大的胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰卧于浩浩碧波之上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受呼伦贝尔最长的日光浴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，仰天高呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍天啊，你怀抱着的星宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未必颗颗都很圣洁——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比如：朱雀、天狼、白虎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用达赉湖的水给她们洗个澡吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样：天上人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会多一些透明度……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}